Subject: Re: [T2] HELP ON ELECTRIC

Find the main wire coming from the back of the bus and test it for 12 volts+ from the wire to the chassis. 

Then check the fuse panel for 12 volts (one side of the fuse to chassis). Also look and see if the ignition switch bundle is getting 12v+ to chassis. That's a big red wire too. 

Chris 
